%% 好友搜索 + 申请 + 接受/拒绝 全流程

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor A as Alice (发起)
    participant HA as pod-X (Alice 连的)
    participant FS as FriendService
    participant UR as UserRepo
    participant FR as FriendshipRepo
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Ev as hubFriendEventPusher
    participant XPod as CrossPodPush
    actor B as Bob (被搜索+接收)

    rect rgb(240,248,255)
        Note over A,B: 阶段 1：搜索用户 GET /api/users/search
        A->>HA: GET /api/users/search?q=bob
        HA->>FS: SearchUsers(q="bob")
        FS->>UR: Search(q)
        UR->>DB: SELECT ... FROM users<br/>WHERE username ILIKE '%bob%' OR display_name ILIKE '%bob%'<br/>LIMIT 20
        DB-->>UR: [{id:B, username:"bob", ...}, ...]
        UR-->>FS: users
        FS-->>HA: users
        HA-->>A: 200 {users:[...]}
    end

    rect rgb(255,248,240)
        Note over A,B: 阶段 2：发送好友申请 POST /api/friends/request
        A->>HA: POST /api/friends/request<br/>{addressee_id: B}
        HA->>FS: SendRequest(A, B)
        FS->>FR: SendRequest(A, B)
        FR->>DB: INSERT friendships<br/>(requester=A, addressee=B, status=pending)
        alt 已存在 (Postgres unique violation 23505)
            DB-->>FR: error: 23505
            FR-->>FS: error
            FS-->>HA: ErrAlreadyExists
            HA-->>A: 409 {"error":"already exists"}
        else 成功
            DB-->>FR: friendship{id:F1, status:pending}
            FR-->>FS: nil
            FS-->>HA: nil
            HA-->>A: 201 {friendship_id:F1}
            HA->>Ev: PushFriendEvent(B, "request", A)
            Ev->>XPod: dispatch(B, TypeFriendEvent, {event_type:"request", from_user_id:A})
            Note over XPod: hub.PushToUser(B) miss<br/>→ routing.Lookup(B) → Bob 所在 pod<br/>→ Pulsar msg.push.{bob-pod}
            XPod->>B: {type:"friend_event", payload:{event_type:"request", from_user_id:A}}
            B->>B: UI 弹出"Alice 想加你为好友"
        end
    end

    rect rgb(240,255,240)
        Note over A,B: 阶段 3：Bob 接受申请 POST /api/friends/accept
        B->>HA: POST /api/friends/accept<br/>{friendship_id: F1}
        HA->>FS: AcceptRequest(F1, B)
        FS->>FR: AcceptRequest(F1, B)
        FR->>DB: UPDATE friendships SET status='accepted'<br/>WHERE id=F1 AND addressee_id=B<br/>RETURNING requester_id
        alt 不是 addressee (Bob 不是被申请方)
            DB-->>FR: RowsAffected=0
            FR-->>FS: repo.ErrNotFound
            HA-->>B: 404
        else 成功
            DB-->>FR: requester_id=A
            FR-->>FS: A
            FS-->>HA: A
            HA-->>B: 200
            HA->>Ev: PushFriendEvent(A, "accepted", B)
            Ev->>XPod: dispatch(A, TypeFriendEvent, {event_type:"accepted", from_user_id:B})
            XPod->>A: {type:"friend_event", payload:{event_type:"accepted", from_user_id:B}}
            A->>A: UI 显示"Bob 接受了你的申请"<br/>好友列表刷新
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255,240,240)
        Note over A,B: 阶段 4（反例）：Bob 拒绝 POST /api/friends/reject
        Note right of B: 流程同阶段 3<br/>但 UPDATE 写 status='rejected'<br/>推 friend_event{event_type:"rejected"} 给 Alice
    end
